{"tid":1465053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟爬山，比意見得但唔好乜都屌咗先(更加唔好屌返轉頭)","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:26.000Z","uid":239129,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f65e517218673923b33107ffe7f68acd9e629669","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"呢幾日開始見到手足之間多咗唔少分歧，唔只局限喺勇武和理非兩大方向，行動上散水唔散水、留唔留公安都幾多唔同聲音。<br />\n<br />\n當然我地要強調不分化不割蓆不譴責，但唔譴責唔代表唔可以比意見嘅。<br />\n只係比意見嘅時候<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要用太重嘅語氣，</span><br />\n而聽嘅都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好即刻就覺得屌緊你/冇用就屌返轉頭，</span><br />\n更<span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要三句唔埋兩句就屌人分化/左膠/冇腦/三毛，</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">火遮眼乜都屌咗先<br />\n先係最分化最撕裂嘅行為。</span></span></strong><br />\n(知你可能冇心但真係會傷士氣)<br />\n相信認真比意見嘅大家都係為件事好，<br />\n唔認真/9up嗰啲我諗大家都分到就唔洗理。<br />\n<br />\n呢個moment，冇大台嘅我地真係<span style=\"color: red;\">每個人都需要盡力保持冷靜去諗多啲反思多啲，</span><br />\nBe humble 比 Be water 更加重要，冇意見個運動又點進步點繼續落去。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">見到有問題有唔妥咪好聲好氣提出下囉，<br />\n有手足覺得有問題咪試下靜落黎諗下囉，<br />\n我地唔可以照顧哂所有人嘅意見但都可以虛心聆聽同有理智咁回覆。</span><br />\n正正係冇大台先要做好啲有效嘅溝通而唔係一味互屌。<br />\n唔好話咩重少少語氣都忍唔到就返歸啦之類，<br />\n呢個時勢大家都好壓抑，<br />\n真係可能一時三刻控制唔到，所以都係想大家多啲提醒下自己。<br />\n明白最近大家可能都陷入情緒低谷，會嬲會灰會燥未必控制到自己，<br />\n但盡力啦，出得黎嘅都係同一條船。<br />\n<br />\n要記住，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇大台下都做到嘅團結先係我地最大嘅武器，</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過兩個幾月嘅抗爭，我見到嘅唔係失敗，<br />\n而係越黎越多人越黎越團結為自己為香港用各種唔同方法發聲，<br />\n唔好喺呢刻先忍唔住心浮氣躁咁互屌互相猜疑，<br />\nkeep住兩個月黎香港人嘅轉變，我地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一<br />\n定<br />\n贏<br />\n撚<br />\n硬</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，兄弟爬山，一齊撐住！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋多謝你睇我廢噏到呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次po長文排版可能7啲唔好見怪"},{"pid":"c17e336283cb62d1ba1082ec04430178fbd80d85","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"ab1ac17b43dc30839bb969320c21ed8a7cc34222","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94179ddebc10e22d52c031fff972a0fc4d7bf072","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580b5aac7c3dbf94b09893efe8e4d02d71efebcc","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bd0369b0eabe86a38590d6ad467221c6f2d38e","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11170667f4d3b4bf40cefc5817ea5602c814e506","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63379b041033c3b879cbbb3c17d06556f408c245","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea27fb78aca5f40b41de607abccbf05e6be9c013","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c489d766fb35414da5316e74e0f6e05504aa6e5","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ce2e418031ffee871f60d3a5f0ec2be1a639c1","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f7d4f4df1a24c7ad7dc2a606df1bab354000ed","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc78e793ec6f64ec1204539a7d5d266979571bb","tid":1465053,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"６１２ ７２１ ８１１！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bc419b0b65955b84eb92571374212b9367a8ad","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1b0ab7d02a27796364ccab86868b5906ad43b1","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"越多越黎突如其來嘅麻煩野發生"},{"pid":"d9f9ad98949d7fee2e1c1e4f6c9fb4026ac61963","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"但唔好乜都互屌先呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7eff1a17f32bb0f0ab5c45aad204cd9ade64c06","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"同一條船呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000d59cc162acbe5c29b95be1f7e4ac92b77af11","tid":1465053,"uid":239129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:49.